sentence: After the Open... Stocks are lower this morning as the market prepares for Apple's ( AAPL ) big presentation.
Home Depot ( HD ) has confirmed that it was hacked , and experts say the data breach may rival Target's ( TGT ) in size.
The market is also watching the move toward Scottish independence very carefully.
Here are your Tuesday morning market metrics.
Industries doing well today include Technology Hardware, Airlines, and Construction Materials.
Industries showing weakness include Personal Products, Electric Utilities, and banks.
The VIX is up 1.3% to 12.83 after closing on Monday at 12.66.
Cheniere Energy ( LNG ) options are being actively traded today, with 9,298 October 85 calls and 9,298 October 80 calls changing hands.
